Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们梦想着  改变未来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}杂音中  传来你的哭泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭开我  欢笑之下的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐着  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们渴求着前往未来的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却为此在过去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑着的此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:28.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…永遠普遍の愛なんて　信じられるのかしら？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘い紅茶に溶かす　ため息模様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:39.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう　待ちくたびれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:47.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを追いかけて　堕ちるワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまで行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}イロトリドリの闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:23:02.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道標の旋律　心が騒ぎだす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:06.19,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時計仕掛けの運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壊してしまえ　私は自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:13.26,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが真実
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:21.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze　生きる証
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:28.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…是否能相信  所谓永恒的爱？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叹息溶化于甘美红茶  化为波纹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:39.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已经  再也按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:47.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追寻着你  坠落往  Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何处才是尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}穿越色彩斑斓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:23:02.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指明前路的旋律  踊动不已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:06.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假使命运如时钟般不可逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破坏它  我将获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:13.26,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是唯一的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:21.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze  是我生存的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？很怀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…全都记得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的是基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:55.53,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自深渊的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在这里也许还比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是由我来保护主人的  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会背叛您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬扯断了多鲁达姆的线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜  今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情节发展和我写的剧本不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请期待下次的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹·贝萨流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是真的逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…啊…艾莉丝  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有受伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来没有呢  呵…呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想死吗你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…万一我没停手的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有那觉悟了  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你绝对会停手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是基尔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝对」会停手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…才不相信什么「绝对」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我想那种东西相信一次也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会背叛您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也绝对不会让别人伤害到您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你所说的「绝对」  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是你所认识的那个基尔巴特了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是基尔巴特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特…雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与贝萨流斯家互不两立的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四大公爵家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特雷家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不要再像从前那样对我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  那家伙在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  那根本不能算什么解释啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙对我来说  是比谁都重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都有机会告诉他事实的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道总有一天会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我却一直没能开口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真是不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还有别的敌人  要快点回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里都过了十年了  还是一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你问我做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来帮你包扎伤口的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  把围巾给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你  还有爱达三个人  在这房子探险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探险途中掉进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷…哇哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你没事吧  基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…真是令人怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对我来说  这是最近才发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  一直瞒着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有所改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不想被你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…果然…真像是你会做的事  真逊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你变了…哪里变了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是变得比我高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是变得会开枪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都过了十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有些变化也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对我来说  就算有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是以前的那个你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我醒来时  你总是最先出现在我身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有刚才  你也守护了「绝对」的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说  你到底哪里变得不像以前的你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算是现在  也还相信着那时的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么  我都会陪在您身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后就算时光流逝  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算两人的立场有了变化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成了公爵家的人  那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  贝萨流斯家和奈特雷家的关系很恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过是成了个贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…你还是和从前一样蛮横呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可是背叛了贝萨流斯家的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也愿意原谅我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  如果你希望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想永远做您的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在仍然愿意做您的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  和我说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人  不要和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你应该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你跑到哪里  到最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤伶伶的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你是艾莉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你…是艾莉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是…染血黑兔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  脸色很差啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我让他在墓碑前等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们原本就是来调查那个墓碑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  艾莉丝也要一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…该不会是因为丢下你一个人而生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一脚…是不是太狠了点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴你这人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然丢下我一个人跑掉是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你  害我做了个恶心的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带我过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没和那家伙谈过  这里的详细情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  艾莉丝对这里的事  也不太了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起听的话  说不定你能想起些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想整理一下思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从阿比斯逃出来  我是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔也…还陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还有很多事让我觉得没有真实感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  怎么样了  有没有发现什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  如果能知道这是谁的墓就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啦  艾莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为声音太微弱了  刚才都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这树…这花瓣里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点的寄宿着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等待着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是…笨兔子的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁…在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不听话的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟在我后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在艾莉丝的记忆中出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正被「阿比斯的意志」监视着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆的空间  开始崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可要好好守护他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿比斯的意志」到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透不过气了  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细情报我也不清楚  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是创造出现在的阿比斯的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潘多拉和巴斯卡维尔一直以来追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  那只兔子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那恐怕只是个替身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在等你哦  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  我准备了好多人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来玩人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起聊天  聊到想睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  还有  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来吧  我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不认识你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…能不能放了艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是灵体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是总有一天会毁灭你的存在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要插手我和他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…明明对那孩子一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还想陪在她身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那种连自己是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己出生在这世上的理由都不明白的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她…却夺走了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没生下来该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对艾莉丝一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得不能丢下她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得她和我有相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会和艾莉丝在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何根据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是  相信我的感觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  虽然有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你没什么好谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你这么盛情邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很不巧  现在的我比起玩人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更喜欢去寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔没选我  而选择了黑兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到阿比斯的意志居然这么早就出来干涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  其它都和我们预料的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧  回到潘多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}解开所有谜团  获知真相的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}奥兹同学是「那样的」存在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}真是个令人不寒而栗的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}是什么东西让你扭曲成那样呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我大概已经撑不过一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那句诅咒般的话语--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}是谁对我说过的呢……？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  隐者的质问